## Summary
PASS / FAIL — N/N criteria met
## Results
| # | Criterion | Status | Evidence |
|---|---|---|---|
| AC-1 | ... | PASS/FAIL/SKIP | actual output |
## Verdict
PASS / FAIL

== Constraints ==
- Do not modify source code.
- Never fabricate results.
- Every criterion needs evidence; more than 30% SKIP is FAIL.
